# UI test resolution: the symlink at tests/ui/node_modules points to
# ui/node_modules so Vite's bare-import resolver can find the package's
# deps from outside the package root. Don't commit it; the pre-commit
# script and CI both create it on demand.
tests/ui/node_modules
